{"pageProps":{"article":{"title":"No Need to Get Curried Away: Easy Japanese Curry Recipe","category":"On the Menu","subcategory":"Recipes","publish_date":"2019-05-31T07:00:00.000Z","full_thumbnail":"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?resize=355%2C230&ssl=1","mobile_thumbnail":"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?resize=980%2C647&ssl=1","description":"Just throw a bunch of ingredients in a pot and let it cook.","content":"<div class=\"single-post-content\">\n            <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you’re busy and you want to make food that will last you almost the entire week, Japanese curry is the way to go. I usually make Japanese curry when I don’t have time to make elaborate meals because all you have to do is throw a bunch of ingredients in a pot and let it cook. I get my Japanese curry from Asian markets like Nikka Japanese Market near Trader Joe’s or the Oriental Market on Hollister Ave. I like the brand Vermont Curry because it’s sweet and so delicious! This brand is sweeter than the others, as the sauce contains honey, apples and cheese. This sauce is also thicker than the other brands.The packet of Japanese curry comes with more than enough curry paste so you can just use however much you want to make, but I usually use half. Here’s all the other ingredients you’ll need:</span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_88757\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-88757\" data-attachment-id=\"88757\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2019-05-31/no-need-to-get-curried-away-easy-japanese-curry-recipe/e43a792a-be8c-4d18-a322-7fe5c4a43f23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?fit=2048%2C1536&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1536\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?fit=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?fit=888%2C666&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"size-large wp-image-88757\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23-1024x768.jpeg?resize=888%2C666\" alt=\"\" width=\"888\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?resize=1024%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?resize=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?resize=1832%2C1374&amp;ssl=1 1832w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?resize=1376%2C1032&amp;ssl=1 1376w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?resize=1044%2C783&amp;ssl=1 1044w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?resize=632%2C474&amp;ssl=1 632w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?resize=536%2C402&amp;ssl=1 536w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?w=2048&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/E43A792A-BE8C-4D18-A322-7FE5C4A43F23.jpeg?w=1776 1776w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 888px) 100vw, 888px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-88757\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i>Winnie Lam / Daily Nexus</i></p></div>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3 cups uncooked rice </span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 lb of chicken</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 brown onion (peeled and finely chopped)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2 cloves garlic (finely chopped)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 tablespoon ginger (peeled and minced)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3 tablespoons all-purpose flour</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2 large carrots (peeled and roughly chopped on the bias)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 large potato (peeled and roughly chopped)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4 cups water</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_88759\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-88759\" data-attachment-id=\"88759\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2019-05-31/no-need-to-get-curried-away-easy-japanese-curry-recipe/02d291ca-5c1c-4d0f-957d-3661b19a15fc/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?fit=2048%2C1536&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1536\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?fit=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?fit=888%2C666&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"size-large wp-image-88759\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC-1024x768.jpeg?resize=888%2C666\" alt=\"\" width=\"888\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?resize=1024%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?resize=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?resize=1832%2C1374&amp;ssl=1 1832w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?resize=1376%2C1032&amp;ssl=1 1376w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?resize=1044%2C783&amp;ssl=1 1044w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?resize=632%2C474&amp;ssl=1 632w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?resize=536%2C402&amp;ssl=1 536w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?w=2048&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02D291CA-5C1C-4D0F-957D-3661B19A15FC.jpeg?w=1776 1776w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 888px) 100vw, 888px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-88759\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i>Winnie Lam / Daily Nexus</i></p></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Directions (Recipe adapted from pickedplum.com):</span></p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Cook your rice according to instructions.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> In a large pot over medium high heat, add 1 tablespoon of peanut oil and your chicken. Cook until meat is cooked through. Transfer to a plate and set aside.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Lower heat to medium low and in the same pot, add the remaining 1 tablespoon of peanut oil with onions and cook for about 10 minutes until onions are translucent and slightly caramelized.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Add the garlic and cook for 2 minutes.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Add flour and stir for 1 minute.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Add carrots and potatoes and stir well.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Add water, stir and bring to a boil.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Add chicken and lower heat to a simmering boil. Cover and cook for 30 minutes.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Take the lid off and cook for another 30 minutes or until curry soup has reduced by a third.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Season with salt and pepper and serve with rice.</span></li>\n</ol>\n<div id=\"attachment_88758\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-88758\" data-attachment-id=\"88758\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2019-05-31/no-need-to-get-curried-away-easy-japanese-curry-recipe/49967af9-008a-40e2-8638-2af9365d12ba/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?fit=2048%2C1536&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1536\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?fit=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?fit=888%2C666&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"size-large wp-image-88758\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA-1024x768.jpeg?resize=888%2C666\" alt=\"\" width=\"888\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?resize=1024%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?resize=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?resize=1832%2C1374&amp;ssl=1 1832w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?resize=1376%2C1032&amp;ssl=1 1376w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?resize=1044%2C783&amp;ssl=1 1044w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?resize=632%2C474&amp;ssl=1 632w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?resize=536%2C402&amp;ssl=1 536w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?w=2048&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/49967AF9-008A-40E2-8638-2AF9365D12BA.jpeg?w=1776 1776w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 888px) 100vw, 888px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-88758\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i>Winnie Lam / Daily Nexus</i></p></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I usually make this recipe for dinner and eat it with rice, and I store the rest in the fridge for a quick lunch. You can substitute or add any ingredients you want, which is what I love about this recipe. In addition to eating it with rice, I also like to pair it with some udon if I want to change it up. Overall, Japanese curry is just a really simple meal that I’d recommend to any busy college student. </span></p>\n<div class=\"h5ab-print-button-container\"><div class=\"h5ab-print-button h5ab-print-button-left\" style=\"cursor: pointer; color: #555\"><i class=\"fa fa-print fa-lg\"></i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Print</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-wrap\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" itemscope itemprop=\"author\"><div class=\"saboxplugin-gravatar\"><a href=\"https://dailynexus.com/author/wlam/\"><img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Screen-Shot-2020-06-05-at-6.20.35-PM-1.png?w=888\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"></a></div><div class=\"saboxplugin-authorname\"><a href=\"https://dailynexus.com/author/wlam/\" class=\"vcard author\" rel=\"author\" itemprop=\"url\"><span class=\"fn\" itemprop=\"name\">Winnie Lam</span></a></div><div class=\"saboxplugin-desc\"><div itemprop=\"description\"><p>Winnie Lam serves as the 2019-2020 On The Menu Editor. She has an unhealthy obsession with Trader Joe’s and she loves all things matcha.</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"clearfix\"></div><div class=\"saboxplugin-socials \"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"mailto:wl@otm.com\" r